<br>
I don't think there's much (or any) benefit over 190 cha, but it's hard for me to say anything for sure about PoP mob encounters, since my Cha is 275 buffed (cap at level 64).  I do think that 160 is the 'critical' mark though. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><br>
